                "text": "Terms & Conditions: This ticket is issued subject to all applicable laws and regulations, and also to the terms and conditions specified in ERL's Conditions of Carriage. Please refer to the website https://kliaekspres.com/conditions-of-carriage/. TICKET USAGE : This is your e-ticket. To use it, please scan this QR Barcode Ticket at the barrier gate. TICKET VALIDITY : The ticket is valid for 31 days from the selected visit date. Ticket validity is stated on your ticket. No refund or exchange will be given for unused trips; no revalidation for expired tickets. No change of travel date once the ticket is issued. TRAIN SERVICE : Ticket is valid for travel on the train service stated on your ticket. TRAIN SCHEDULE : Please refer https://kliaekspres.com/schedule/ for updated train schedule and service frequency."
